HEADWORD: Retrait
<hw>Re*trait"</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*tr⟦amac⟧t")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It.
<ets>ritratto</ets>, fr. <ets>ritrarre</ets> to draw back, draw, fr. L.
<ets>retrahere</ets>. See <er>Retract</er>.]</ety> <def>A portrait; a
likeness.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whose fair <qex>retrait</qex> I in my shield do bear.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
